This is a placeholder for the Twitter Card image (1200x600px).

To create the actual image:
1. Create a 1200x600px PNG image
2. Include the app name "Markdown Typing SVG"
3. Add a tagline like "Create Animated SVGs for Your README"
4. Show an example of the typing SVG animation
5. Use brand colors (indigo/purple gradient)
6. Ensure text is readable on the background
7. Save as twitter-image.png in the public folder

Example design elements:
- Gradient background: from-indigo-500 to-purple-600
- White text with shadow for readability
- Keyboard/typing icon or animation preview
- Clean, modern design
- App logo or icon in corner
- Optimized for Twitter's card display
